      "id": "PopularPost281504",
      "post_content": "This card is a great example of how to make a powerful card without breaking it. Give it a powerful effect, namely, tapping for mana, make it free to play, and let the player have as many as they want in a deck. Limit its effectiveness by only allowing one to be played every turn. Make it more relevant again by making it immune to almost all forms of destruction. Truly an enabler of many a red deck out there. ",
      "posted_by": "Dannyman658",
